{"tid":1546360,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"圍緊太子嘅同我入嚟!! 地鐵員工教路（一手）","createTime":"2019-09-06T09:02:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T12:15:58.000Z","uid":19804,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"ab9a513a05276a33c1b2dc61ced28e36b002230a","tid":1546360,"uid":19804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T09:02:40.000Z","msg":"地鐵員工教路（一手）<br />\n<br />\n💥太子站嘅員工只係前線基層員工，無人會夠膽攞條片出黎<br />\n💥所有cctv 嘅file 都係儲存係青衣控制中心嘅server 度<br />\n💥所以要圍就應該圍青衣控制中心‼<br />\n（青衣城有間唐記包點泰昌餅家嗰個位，有兩隻鋼門係有閉路電視撳鐘佢會問你係邊個）<br />\n<br />\n記住：青衣控制中心先係成個車務嘅主宰，佢話晒事，邊個車站清客、飛站、關閉站、行唔行車，全部都係嗰邊話事‼<br />\n<br />\n另外，唔好同人講：<br />\n青衣機鐵站，的士上客嗰邊都有個停車場，係控制中心啲同事泊車用😌"},{"pid":"d6ac63dfdb6c6f5d99d881b05a70c839a21b48c8","tid":1546360,"uid":76702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T09:03:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"99f5162908fe1c03a9689ba8bf40b4031fa22ee6","tid":1546360,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T09:03:35.000Z","msg":"7/9機場更新 求求大家<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1545323\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1545323</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Fg5HKFh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFg5HKFh.jpg&h=b79850f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=%2B76N%2F2LucaPHjeWFFloOr9Dxg6radaiL0c7rOhjaEfM%3D&h=c68d1128\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a>"},{"pid":"53a0d3ef740aa47e3726cb152bed0df23bf60f8a","tid":1546360,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T09:04:00.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi